# Sellsuki Design System — Windsurf Rules
# Full spec: https://sellsukidesignsystemv12.vercel.app/ai-rules.md

## Required Setup (ALWAYS do this first)
```bash
npm install @uxuissk/design-system@0.7.2
npm install @uxuissk/design-tokens@0.1.1  # optional
```

```tsx
// main.tsx — MUST be the FIRST import
import "@uxuissk/design-system/styles.css";
import { DSButton, DSInput, Card, AdvancedDataTable, TopNavbar, Sidebar } from "@uxuissk/design-system";
```

⚠️ CRITICAL: Without `import "@uxuissk/design-system/styles.css"`:
- DB HeaventRounded font will NOT load
- All `var(--text-*)` size tokens will be undefined (render as 0px)
- Components will appear visually broken

## Font — DB HeaventRounded
- Applied to: ALL text elements — headings, body, labels, buttons, badges, nav items, table cells, sidebar
- NEVER use: Inter, Roboto, system-ui, or any other font
- Source: bundled in npm package via @font-face in styles.css

## Typography Tokens (use these, never px values)
```
var(--text-h1)      → 48px / weight 400
var(--text-h2)      → 40px / weight 400
var(--text-h3)      → 28px / weight 700
var(--text-h4)      → 24px / weight 500
var(--text-p)       → 20px / weight 400  ← default body
var(--text-label)   → 18px / weight 400  ← form labels, UI labels
var(--text-button)  → 18px / weight 600  ← buttons, badges, tabs
var(--text-caption) → 14px / weight 400  ← MINIMUM SIZE — never smaller
```

## Colors (CSS vars preferred over hex)
```
var(--primary)        → #32a9ff  (Sky-500) — buttons, links
var(--primary-hover)  → #1b8bf5  (Sky-600) — hover
var(--foreground)     → #1f2937  (Gray-800) — body text
var(--muted-foreground) → #6b7280 (Gray-500) — muted text
var(--border)         → #e5e7eb  (Gray-200) — dividers
var(--background)     → #fff
var(--surface)        → #f9fafb  (Gray-50)
```

## Spacing
- Page padding: 24px desktop / 16px mobile
- Card/form gap: 16px
- Section gap: 32px
- Border radius: 8px default

